================= Flow ===================
- developer push code ke github
- jenkins clone repo ke workspace
- ada security  scanning
    - owasp: dependency vulnerabilities
    - Trivy File Scan: scan source code/filesystem
    - SonarQube: scan kualitas & bug kode
- kode passed lanjut build image, push ke hub
- Trivy scan docker image
- deploy ke container
- deploy to EKS pakai file K8S/deployment.yml